cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM 

This paper is primarily focused on crowd counting, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also proposes a novel adversarial learning approach, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of pyramid patches and multi-scale inputs suggests the involvement of neural networks (cs.NE) and the evaluation of the proposed method on unseen datasets involves metrics and analysis (cs.MM).
